{"tid":980333,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱好辛苦","createTime":"2019-01-13T12:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T03:21:37.000Z","uid":179630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5060b896b36fa353a982da2b87b71990dcb5377f","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"每次抑鬱發作就會自己一個出街飲酒鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺街喊完頹完返屋企咁又冇咗一日，浪費咗咁多時間乜都冇做就更加頹，越覺得自己一事無成就越sad，日日係咁loop好辛苦"},{"pid":"c28311ee448c8a3828812a58a9cb902b7dbe4927","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"本身自己有抑鬱，屋企人情緒病又越嚟越嚴重，又唔知點開口勸佢睇醫生，呀媽對住屋企人個個都有情緒病真係覺得佢好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07b6215f727cc14e711a80bd0d514cb8f46477d","tid":980333,"uid":230137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2de332275870b19a3cd6369dd1902775f845260c","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07b6215f727cc14e711a80bd0d514cb8f46477d","tid":980333,"uid":230137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"我係遺傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以屋企除咗呀媽之外都有情緒病"},{"pid":"6ac5b886b47ab4659f94e649b512b6b48827f729","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"我鍾意嘅男仔知我有病之後有約我出嚟傾偈，之前同佢表白拒絕過我。雖然佢會約我真係好開心，但係我唔想佢係因為個病而可憐我嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10142c308ab858af19c8997a9668ab37ed4d036a","tid":980333,"uid":111625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"自從我比人綠左之後,轉左新工好冇乜野做,每日都來回諗起唔開心既野,已經10個月,醫生話我壓力大有抑鬱,但其實自己好明白,依加連同D同學正常溝通都做唔到,比人當左我性格有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c8fb80fcf58fdf8f9c98decf8d1650692ce01c","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10142c308ab858af19c8997a9668ab37ed4d036a","tid":980333,"uid":111625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"自從我比人綠左之後,轉左新工好冇乜野做,每日都來回諗起唔開心既野,已經10個月,醫生話我壓力大有抑鬱,但其實自己好明白,依加連同D同學正常溝通都做唔到,比人當左我性格有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192941f1cd9b519d000ff989ee770d8c5b167257","tid":980333,"uid":61392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"每日都想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65daefc434a025206e146aa9ede0776179744b7f","tid":980333,"uid":224847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"有冇搵過人傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa5e82091d0160432d0d2609f3417e0253b3ea7","tid":980333,"uid":224847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de332275870b19a3cd6369dd1902775f845260c","tid":980333,"uid":179630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07b6215f727cc14e711a80bd0d514cb8f46477d","tid":980333,"uid":230137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"我係遺傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以屋企除咗呀媽之外都有情緒病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"咁遺傳係Sad 啲～！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df4014a22a98640917f37006396d33567a39536","tid":980333,"uid":224847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de332275